{"type": "article", "id": 51458, "title": "一款表达爱意的项链，爱只有佩戴的人才能看到｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-03-25T23:16:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 48705, "name": "JHO Knives"}, {"id": 39083, "name": "Gufram"}, {"id": 48706, "name": "PLEASE DO NOT ENTER"}, {"id": 48707, "name": "Gejst"}, {"id": 48708, "name": "Lucas Muñoz"}, {"id": 48709, "name": "Dario Narvaez"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 201, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180325223623wRDfPlTziIXLgHGr.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s7 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s9 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s10 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s11 {font-kerning: none; color: #a4a1a1; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #a4a1a1} span.s12 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s13 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Flex Line of Wall-Mounted Storage by Gejst</h3><p>丹麦家居品牌 Gejst 推出了一款多功能的墙面储物架 Flex，意在满足人们在紧凑空间中更多的存储需求。Flex 可以灵活组合使用，适用于包括书房、卧室以及厨房等家中的任何空间，用户可以随意移动以及添加或移除任何可用的组件。</p><p>一旦将导轨固定在合适的墙壁位置，用户就可以使用包括挂钩、盒子、托盘、货架在内的任何配件，组装使用。售价 20 欧元起，<a href=\"https://gejst.com/produkt-tag/flex-en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223806gzs0QtpPvnmcArlb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.856250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223806ZGJBtbe4AIMiSpWl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.554688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803252238067fVR4PU0zKpHTDkM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.949219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223807U5y6roH9ql0V34jN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.317969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223807OjlQyXRuTFb7JMV9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803252238070pWI6wEKqeMlHPJh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223807VZhuOKbwsHdDzRQM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Da Vetro Collection by Fabrica Research Center for PLEASE DO NOT ENTER</h3><p>PLEASE DO NOT ENTER 是一家以艺术展览为主的零售精品店。最近来自意大利 Fabrica 研究中心的一群年轻设计师，为其量身定制了一组名为 Da Vetro 的花瓶、玻璃瓶和容器的限量版系列作品，据说是受到人类手势和姿态的启发。</p><p>Da Vetro 系列共有八种设计，均由意大利玻璃工匠 Massimo Lunardon 手工吹制而成，每种设计只能限量制作 30 件。</p><p>比如立陶宛设计师 Lukas Valiauga 设计的一款拥有未来主义风格的 308s，看上去像是一个沙漏计时器。</p><p>意大利设计师 Elena Bompani 的作品 Slipped My Mind 主体受到人体胸部形状的启发，手柄部分则是受到面部轮廓的启发，暗指记忆像鲜花的生命一样短促等等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223904t3BMZpWv2hGgXAuS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335156\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/collection-glass-vessels-inspired-gestures-postures/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223904mpBJY5rvxUjgFdON.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803252239050zgewYxWBus7U8Mo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223905IRjgPkdQCLJ8EUHs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223906vuL3ONEJXzpSBRtV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223906LxoOS5uZBwKHGypn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223907aHIdxskhLAvSYJM3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803252239062CvTgfhrzpldxi6B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803252239079vAOeu4dkn3zCKBp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Invisible Love Necklace by Dario Narvaez</h3><p>纽约工业设计师 Dario Narvaez 推出了一款名为 Invisible Love 的项链，跨越传统项链样式，试图探索光、影和形状的互动关系，赋予作品纯粹、干净的样式。制造惊喜是设计中的关键元素，当光线从正确的角度照到圆环上时，它会在圆柱体上形成一个心形的阴影，这个阴影可以被所有人看到，或者通过翻转主体，仅由佩戴它的人来看。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=v0613b4e2fi&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t<figcaption class=\"\">视频来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/dario-narvaez-minimal-necklace-light-hidden-message-03-24-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223953pAtPXZyhi2kHlMcz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.589242\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223953tpv8B7cfkELRPhNC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.589242\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223954a0qyQF1LzbGfrOYv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.589242\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223955M8H2PjXEJsD0TAdp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.589242\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325223956pFDOlCvxRiNdVwJ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.589242\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/dario-narvaez-minimal-necklace-light-hidden-message-03-24-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Tubular Chair by Lucas Muñoz</h3><p>埃因霍温设计师 Lucas Muñoz 将工业钢制通风管道与从垃圾场拿回来的铜制座椅结合在一起，制造出这款名为 Tubular 的球形座椅。</p><p>在设计师看来，有些工业部件是很实用的，如果能够按照家庭环境提供某种家具功能的方式对其进行再设计，或许可以在当代家居环境中扮演重要角色。就像这个镀锌钢制通风管道和从垃圾场捡回来的铜片，原本是不可能出现在家中的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325224059smqjpuzx1bZEgGdB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325224101ImdJ5PrjXnAfuNyG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803252241021Fxb0LXNuCeUJzw6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.238156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803252241053CMvH0m4dkoVFBbS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.265651\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Disco Gufram Collection by Atelier Biagetti, Dutch designers Rotganzen, and Paris-based studio GGSV for Gufram</h3><p>在下个月的米兰国际家具展上，意大利家具品牌 Gufram 为向品牌辉煌的过去致敬，会推出名为 Disco Gufram 的家具系列，通过一系列灵感来源于迪斯科的家具作品，追溯到 1960-70 年代意大利激进设计最鼎盛的时期。</p><p>参与设计的是 Atelier Biagetti，荷兰设计师 Rotganzen 和巴黎工作室 GGSV。比如将 1970 年代的软垫迪斯科沙发进行重新诠释，将其转化为五款不同坐具，既向经典致敬，同时展示出独有的现代风格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325224144nKZQ4Y0HE6LcrUlG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325224145txqc97ObinkgFwz8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803252241462IVwtvp3UsyjDZE5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325224147udLWzvlhieXRYSsa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325224148JHM7yf5N0w9pTsgq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>BLANKA by JHO Knives</h3><p>BLANKA 是一款迷你切肉刀，整个刀恰好能够握在手掌中，看起来很 Q，适合女性用户使用，但切肉能力却丝毫不比传统的切肉刀差。</p><p>由 VG-10 日本钢制成的刀片和日式 tanto 刀片，可以让刀片的前缘作为刀刃，保证 BLANKA 的灵活性，便于用户以任何方式抓握它，也便于施力。此外，这把刀还配有专门的挂绳孔以及一个皮套。售价 205 美元，<a href=\"https://jho-knives.com/products/blanka\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325224237vK1nLblwXTtgDZif.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325224237GP6ZuJfMzrjoCQB9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325224238Hq3L1aDVUJZXFx2f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325224238tU0OwSaLFqXkepbD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325224238btx0YM62myRhvB59.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180325224240ixSktdmaWeBI0bC1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803252242400IhPEXp4dSayxKLn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://jho-knives.com/products/blanka\" rel=\"nofollow\">JHO Knives</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}